<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="born-vt">born <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɔːn/    美 /bɔːrn/  </p>
<p>[只用于被动语态，不与by连用]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>出生；诞生：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>was born into</strong> a musical family.
她生于一个音乐世家。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>were born with</strong> some rare talent. 
他们生来就具有某种罕见的才能。</p><footer> 2013 广东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>产生；出现；形成</strong></h4>
<p>to start to exist：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His wish to become a doctor <strong>was born (out) of</strong> a desire to help sick people. 
他想当医生的愿望源于他想帮助病人。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>…出生的；…产生的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My parents have raised twelve kids and I am their <strong>first-born</strong> son. 
我父母养育了12个孩子，我是他们的长子。</p><footer>2014 广东改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-born-to-do-be-sth">be born to do / be sth</h3>
<p>1.<strong>天生适合做某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was born to be a politician. 
他天生就是个政治家。</p></div></div>